name: Ardulink
tagline: A library for Arduino Simulink comunication.
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
Ardulink is the aim of becoming a good tool between Arduino and Simulink, helping the community in solving engineering problems to getting data with your microcontroller. The library was made ​​in order to be fully effective without any complicated setup too Simulink.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
